To use the applet you can use this in a HTML document:
copy the archive JWebcamPlayer.jar and control.jpg to your http root directory
Then insert the following code in your html document index.html
if the spcaserv run on the same linux box nothing to change in the following code:)

<applet codebase="." archive="JWebcamPlayer.jar" code="JWebcamPlayer/JWebcamPlayer.class" name="JWebcamPlayer" ID="JWebcamPlayer" width="400" height="400" MAYSCRIPT>
<param name="Color" value="#ffffff">
<param name="Server" value="127.0.0.1">
<param name="Port" value="7070">
<PARAM NAME="scriptable" value="true">
<PARAM NAME="mayscript" value="true">
<strong>You need to download Java.<br>
Click <a href="http://www.java.com/en/download/manual.jsp">here:
http://www.java.com/en/download/manual.jsp</a></strong><br>
</applet>
 
